</Turn>
<Turn speaker="spk2" startTime="988.046" endTime="1011.992" fidelity="high">
<Sync time="988.046"/>
Ne, takrat nisem razmišljali o tem. #Eee, 
<Sync time="991.619"/>
ko si star dvajset let, #eee, 
<Sync time="993.553"/>
